src_text: As NSA, he assisted Carter in diplomatically handling world affairs, such as the Camp David Accords, 1978; normalizing US–China relations thought the late 1970s; the Iranian Revolution, which led to the Iran hostage crisis, 1979; and the Soviet invasion in Afghanistan, 1979.
ref_text: Na Iyya NSA, Alena nabantu Carter ri lalenna passilolongang urusang lino, sippada sipaturukenna Camp David, 1978, na padecengngi hubunganna US-China di cappa'na taung 1970-ang; repolusi Iran, iya paccapparenna ko maegana tau mancaji tahanang Iran, 1979, na nalokkaini Soviet ko Afghanistan, 1979.
hyp_text: Séna NSA, iya pahapé Carter ri diplomasé wala'ng afé, tahu' Camp David Accords, 1978; normalisasi US-China, tahu' akhir 1970; revolusi Iran, tahu' pahapé Iran hostage crisis, 1979; na Soviet invasion Afghanistan, 1979.

src_text: Most interpretations of technological determinism share two general ideas: that the development of technology itself follows a path largely beyond cultural or political influence, and that technology in turn has "effects" on societies that are inherent, rather than socially conditioned.
ref_text: Maéga passitujung ripakullei ri teknologi makkéda èngka  dua idé umum: iyanaritu parkembanganna teknologi é mabéla polé pengaruhna ade’é na politik é, na iyyatu teknologi wedding nappengarui keadaanna masyarakat yaro inheren é na de'gaga pengarunna lao ri masyarakat yari rikondisikan secara sosial.
hyp_text: Riolo makké-ke' kabaré teknologi determinisme rupa'ba' dua ide' umum: na teknologi iya tugasna tulusna' ri lolo' kabaré-kabaré kultura' na politik, na teknologi iya tugasna 'pahati' na masyarakat iya tulusna', na'ngka tulusna' ma'ngka tulusna'.
